61
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,500
Sister.

62
00:06:36,210 --> 00:06:36,980
Ginseng.

63
00:06:58,220 --> 00:06:58,750
Warrior.

64
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,710
What's your name, warrior?

65
00:07:00,810 --> 00:07:02,340
