78
00:07:27,660 --> 00:07:28,460
Otherwise,

79
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:32,700
Wenren Jing is dead meat.

80
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:36,330
Lu Tingxiao, if you cut off your meridians,

81
