82
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:38,980
Three.

83
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:42,580
Two.

84
00:07:44,930 --> 00:07:45,740
Warrior.

85
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:47,600
Warrior, listen to me.

86
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:49,140
If you kill me,

87
00:07:49,900 --> 00:07:51,760
